2,000 lb Mini Excavator

CAT CLASS: 0350110
2,000 lb Mini Excavator
-
1 DAY
-
1 WEEK
-
4 WEEK
The 2,000 lb mini excavator is an excellent option for smaller projects. With a peak digging force of 1,865 lbs and outstanding maneuverability, the compact excavator has a maximum digging depth of 6 feet, as well as, a reach of 11 feet. These mini excavators features rubber tracks and a backfill blade for leveling and stabilizing ground. Renting a mini excavator is an excellent solution for digging around obstacles or alongside structures for small size jobs.

Products are subject to availability.
